{"data":[{"id":561549899,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"5974e58382034822e7920b76ab3410fd","url_token":"tao-lei-yi","name":"是阿毅啊","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-d563584020b0bf9cfaed1b354c7dbf1d_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-d563584020b0bf9cfaed1b354c7dbf1d_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/5974e58382034822e7920b76ab3410fd","user_type":"people","headline":"执着于PPT的PPT菜鸟","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561549899","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545977722,"updated_time":1545977722,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":6,"content":"\u003cp\u003e如果题主真能证明得出，我就在本回答的评论中随机抽中一位关注我的知友，赠送iPhonexs一台，绝不食言。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563796204,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"608b8c227d6a19469238c96eb0853b86","url_token":"li-xian-6-14-15","name":"退乎","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-59f01059f8faf1a36330cd35e47fe5b8_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-59f01059f8faf1a36330cd35e47fe5b8_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/608b8c227d6a19469238c96eb0853b86","user_type":"people","headline":"逐步删除所有回答、收藏，退乎","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563796204","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-2eed6f3a2473ed0a9e0c45d80cb1fd5a_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546278451,"updated_time":1546278451,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":6,"content":"\u003cp\u003e\u003ca class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hash=\"7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\"\u003e@证明\u003c/a\u003e \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e该证明是错的，图中标注部分有逻辑问题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e作者把-1加到了质数的集合中，为避免偷换概念，我们把这个新集合叫B数。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e原命题即为若-1是B数，则巴拉巴拉。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e此时该命题的前件为真，所以命题真假取决与后件巴拉巴拉的真假。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e逆否命题为若巴拉巴拉，则-1不是B数。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e在作者假设的前提下，该逆否命题后件为假，只有前件为假时，该逆否命题才为作者想要的真。即问题实质转换为证明前件为假，显然若证存在xxx，巴拉巴拉为假，需证所有的xxx，都不巴拉巴拉。作者这一翻折腾并没有任何意义。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e即便是有可能用特例证明逆否命题，他证明逆否命题时这是怎么提的特例，亮瞎了我的钛合金狗眼。若存在x，满足一个条件的特例应该是找到一个x，满足该条件，他这是什么东西，还把如果那么带下来了？？#黑人问号脸.jpeg\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e注:前件为假时，不论后件真假，命题均为真。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-2eed6f3a2473ed0a9e0c45d80cb1fd5a_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1536\" data-rawheight=\"2048\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-d05b0842438170c7891904da0686d2bf_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1536\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-2eed6f3a2473ed0a9e0c45d80cb1fd5a_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1536'%20height='2048'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1536\" data-rawheight=\"2048\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-d05b0842438170c7891904da0686d2bf_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1536\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-2eed6f3a2473ed0a9e0c45d80cb1fd5a_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-2eed6f3a2473ed0a9e0c45d80cb1fd5a_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562783325,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562783325","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-e88feffac997130323b05eb9d359c467_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546145719,"updated_time":1546145867,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":6,"content":"\u003cp\u003e呦，真巧，我这几天也刚刚证出来。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hash=\"7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\"\u003e@证明\u003c/a\u003e 你说咱俩会不会就像牛顿和莱布尼兹一样，因为谁先创立了微积分的问题而争论不休呢？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-e291370985c2226d650207f922239b51_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"104\" data-rawheight=\"80\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"104\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='104'%20height='80'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"104\" data-rawheight=\"80\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"content_image lazy\" width=\"104\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-e291370985c2226d650207f922239b51_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e话说在前头，虽说你先声称自己证明出来了，但我的方法更胜一筹，绝对比你用的方法简洁。所以后人应该先提我的名字。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-c040b3620da1c4fca6520b22b1fbb58c_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"340\" data-rawheight=\"287\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-c040b3620da1c4fca6520b22b1fbb58c_b.jpg\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"340\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='340'%20height='287'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"340\" data-rawheight=\"287\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-c040b3620da1c4fca6520b22b1fbb58c_b.jpg\" class=\"content_image lazy\" width=\"340\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-c040b3620da1c4fca6520b22b1fbb58c_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e好了，废话不多说，我的证明如下：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e首先，不妨先假设哥德巴赫猜想成立。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e那么，根据假设可知，哥德巴赫猜想成立。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e证明完毕。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e简洁不简洁？思路是不是很清楚？你说我牛逼不牛逼？哈哈，我都佩服我自己。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e致后人：\u003c/b\u003e记得到时候提哥德巴赫猜想的时候，把我的名字放在“证明”老哥前面啊。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e不说了，陪老婆去了。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e攒石党求求求求求求求欧气！！！\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e愿我单抽出阿比！单抽出艾蕾！单抽出黑贞！\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-c996cc3bf1af0c6fbaab94ba3cb22ebf_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"727\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-c996cc3bf1af0c6fbaab94ba3cb22ebf_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-c996cc3bf1af0c6fbaab94ba3cb22ebf_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='720'%20height='727'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"727\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-c996cc3bf1af0c6fbaab94ba3cb22ebf_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-c996cc3bf1af0c6fbaab94ba3cb22ebf_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-c996cc3bf1af0c6fbaab94ba3cb22ebf_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560477990,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0e39f0dad25386e8916fd2222eb93f78","url_token":"mi-ze-54","name":"Thaumiel","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-5eb0af43a54f4d67512614b5fe07c21a_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-5eb0af43a54f4d67512614b5fe07c21a_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0e39f0dad25386e8916fd2222eb93f78","user_type":"people","headline":"笑骂由之，我自为之","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560477990","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545841065,"updated_time":1545841065,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":6,"content":"\u003cp\u003e“我也想到了一种美妙的证明方法，可是知乎格子太小，写不下”\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563793868,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"update