没啥意思，想看一下你的手速有多快。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563792111,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"3278a324de072edcda4031440eb079dd","url_token":"","name":"知乎用户","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":true},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563792111","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546277795,"updated_time":1546277795,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":6,"content":"\u003cp\u003e刚刚看了他的证明，虽然是数学外行，但看他这解题篇幅几页演算纸搞定就说明几乎不可能成功。提问者保送清华北大是不可能了，但是以后有时间了可以去北京到以上两所大学参观旅游。\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e前几天一直抱着期望的态度等着今天的结果…\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e也算是意料之中吧。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e最后说一句话：提问者还是高中生，\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003ci\u003e无知者无畏\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/b\u003e。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e骂他的、说要人肉他的有点过分了。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563479369,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"foll