46ba3b03c3047f_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-6ba6752a31041746eb46ba3b03c3047f_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/2097a8b4740391cb861b7137a22b516a","user_type":"people","headline":"现役（蒟蒻）MOer","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560767263","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545886060,"updated_time":1546330462,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":7,"content":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e已注销\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e2019首答\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e恭喜题主已具备了民科的姿态\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e在完全没搞清楚质数定义的情况下进行了诡辩\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e取关啦 告辞\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e顺便挂题主证明的逻辑错误(见另一个问题)\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e年前原回答：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e还是再找几个数学专家确认一下吧\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e天才少年被众多知友打击也怪可惜的\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e可能你用了什么你感觉很显然但是实际上也很难证明的定理呢\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e千万 千万不要走向民科坑\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560601503,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560601503","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545873074,"updated_time":1545873074,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":7,"content":"\u003cp\u003e印象中第一次知乎回答\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e以下答案的前提建立在\"题主认真提问\"且身份确实\"老师\"所说的高中生\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e看了很多回答，大多是给题主泼冷水的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e为什么大家要打击一个对数学充满热爱的高中生的信心？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e为什么大家不相信题主所述？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e题主说的有没有可能？高中生有没有可能证出\"哥德巴赫猜想\"？\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2\u003e可能。\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003e但可能性微乎其微。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e为什么这么说？且不说\u003cb\u003e多少数学家数学研究工作者投入其中多少时光都未能解决\u003c/b\u003e，也不谈它需要\u003cb\u003e多么坚实渊博的数学知识\u003c/b\u003e，我们假设，假设题主知识水平达到了解决\"哥德巴赫猜想\"的要求，也确确实实解决了这个猜想。那么，题主\u003cb\u003e会不会疑惑于\"能不能保送清北\"，会不会\"考个211 985都难\"，会不会\"偏科\"？\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我觉得，大家不信任题主，甚至于讽刺题主，后者的怀疑占得更多。\u003cb\u003e简言之，题主的思想状况不符合解决\"哥猜\"的人的思想状况，解决了猜想的人，不应该会在知乎提出这样的问题。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e即使你失败了，发现自己的证明错了，也不必悲伤，不必自责\u003c/b\u003e，不过是变成\"高中生证明哥德巴赫猜想失败\"而已，不会有人笑话你。\u003cb\u003e你还年轻，还有很多时间去经历\u003c/b\u003e，不是吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果你能静下心来，能明白\u003cb\u003e自己需要的其实并不是\"证猜想上清北\"\u003c/b\u003e，那这篇回答我就写得值了。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563806528,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"fec88b914b1ceb11d27bcf121c160694","url_token":"luo-kai-teng-57","name":"Geoge","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-9e628430a676ebace94dc610fc9377c1_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-9e628430a676ebace94dc610fc9377c1_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/fec88b914b1ceb11d27bcf121c160694","user_type":"people","headline":"咸鱼","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563806528","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546280458,"updated_time":1546280635,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":5,"content":"我原以为证明过程就算没有一本笔记本，也有半本，万万没想到挤一挤的话一页纸大概都写不满……心情复杂 ","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562600846,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"8dfa05cbe4a4e8aa0253fc367b79626b","url_token":"xie-dong-liu-25","name":"叶东流","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-4a4fdd24d966ec532764c7696fa47cef_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-4a4fdd24d966ec532764c7696fa47cef_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/8dfa05cbe4a4e8aa0253fc367b79626b","user_type":"people","headline":"自由而无用的灵魂","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562600846","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546107156,"updated_time":1546279019,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":5,"content":"\u003cp\u003e修改回答：题主可能真的是神经有点问题，我对鼓励态度持保留意见。（手动滑稽）\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e先摆观点：就现在来看，这位同学确实有些不知天高地厚了。不过我们如果嘲讽打击，确实也不应当。把事情讲明白，道理讲清楚，就好，他接不接受那又是另一回事了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这个其实 \u003ca class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/77fa6383d2443330fb7550edf64e1b19\" data-hash=\"77fa6383d2443330fb7550edf64e1b19\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$77fa6383d2443330fb7550edf64e1b19\"\u003e@Vayne嫒\u003c/a\u003e 这位答主的回答说得很好，高中只是大学的敲门砖，大学才是学术之门的敲门砖，进了学术之门才可能看见哥猜的大门，至于能不能敲开就是你的本事了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e到现在，看了很久的戏，也吃了许多瓜，还是忍不住要写点东西。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e首先声明，我不是学数学的，也不是学理工医科的，不过我们可以类比。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e一句证明哥猜相当于什么？各位可以看下面三句话：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e①我释读出了十个甲骨文，过几天给你们看，有理有据。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e②我能给自由意志与恶的问题做一个逻辑完整自洽的公理化分析，过几天你们看。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e③我挖出了虞墟，证明了二里头之前的中国北方有国家形态的文明，过几天给你们看考古报告。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e①，自从清末民国以来，中国无数文字学家、训诂学家、考据学家、考古学家都想多释读一个甲骨文，现在已经到了瓶颈。别说释读出来了，提出一个有道理的猜想就可以学界瞩目了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e②，吵了一千五百年以上的问题，无数哲学家、神学家试图给出一个解答，但到现在为止，没有一个逻辑是没有漏洞的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e③，中国人心心念念几千年的事情，现代考古学研究了几十年的事情，夏商周断代工程都做白了一群人的头发，你说挖出虞墟是不是可以让世界震动？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e尽管如此，我还是知道上面三句话的分量其实不会重于证出哥猜，哥猜是数学的皇冠明珠，在许多人看来更有一种神圣性。可能只有自由意志的问题对本学界的学者具有同样的神圣性了。要证出哥猜，需要的智慧也许还要超过你编出一个能蒙骗万千世人的虞墟。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我们说文人相轻，特别他还是一个名不见经传的高中生，那么他被一群人嘲讽也是正常，不加以打击的话如何显示其所学的专业性？实话说，要是哪个高中生说“我能给古代汉语重新断代，而且证据充足，可以取代现行的几个体系”估计我也会上去骂一顿，人家王力高本汉郑张尚芳那么多大师都扯不清楚的你算个什么？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e确实，劝诫和说理就足够了，讽刺还是有些过了。不过我们也要想到一个问题，有些人学了专业数学，甚至就是学数学专业的，当他们看到这么一个可以说是不知天高地厚的回答时，他一定会产生“这个人在侮辱数学界的皇冠明珠”的想法，也难怪他们要讽刺。至于那些毫无知识背景就讽刺的，大家就当是抬杠了，看着好玩随手评几句，其它别管了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e最后还是希望题主能先想办法进入学术的领域再思考证明哥猜的问题。如果题主都进不了这个领域，那么你证出的可能性大概就是零，那种几何概型里点到一个点的概率，而被众人舆论消费的可能性是一。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563777594,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"2c5ffee825b6e736c7f5841b18c899f6","url_token":"lyh5211314-44","name":"刘宇辉","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-7cfc6255fb54e17c82366d2b2608729a_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-7cfc6255fb54e17c82366d2b2608729a_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/2c5ffee825b6e736c7f5841b18c899f6","user_type":"people","headline":"一枝独秀，拒绝合群。要一起也是和秀儿们一起。","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563777594","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546275729,"updated_time":1546307104,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":5,"content":"\u003cp\u003e2n+1是质数？？！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e质数：自然数中除1外，只能被一和自己整除的数\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e先不说负质数和假设的逻辑问题\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你这个\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e三三得九\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e三五十五\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e三七二十一\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e三九二十七\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e总会吧？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你n是4的时候9为什么是质数？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e卒。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e麻烦下一个秀智商的“证明”可以“抄袭”大牛的论文。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e（虽然我很讨厌抄袭）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e然而你这样是把别人当傻x玩\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e同九年，何汝秀？\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559931228,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559931228","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545794641,"updated_time":1545794904,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":5,"content":"\u003cp\u003e1月1号发证明过程。。。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e看出来了，你无非就是想火一把。现在这流量的世道，美也好，丑也罢，只要哗众成功了，赚钱的机会就来了。相比较而言，用丑的一面博眼球更简单更容易。以前的什么凤姐，某手里的一些用户，都是这么起来的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我估计你的想法差不多就是这样。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e多少年前看的一篇名为“审丑”的文章，其实真的早就应验了。你如果选对了路，靠这个未必不能火一把。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但是找哥猜这种东西想火，真是滑稽。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e首先关注这个的人虽然很多，但一般都是学术界的或者民科偏多，民科基本上不会搭理你，他们忙着用自己的方法证明呢。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e学术界的，除非你真的证出来了，不然，一份疑似民科的“证明“，不好意思，没人会搭理你的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e没有得到权威承认的证明，大众根本不会关注，因为这种所谓的证明，真的是网上一搜一大把。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e本身受众就小，加上太多的可重复性，这个话题压根没一点吸收流量的能力，营销号什么的也根本不会去带节奏，因为资本不会做这种明显亏本的生意。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e客观来说，你这一套行动下来，也就用“一月一日发证明”这个造势的行为能勉强吸一点流量。但是也只能如此了，此事过后，说不定也能成个过千粉的“大V”。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但是没有其他产出，加上热闹看完了，估计粉慢慢也就掉完了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e综上，奉劝一句，你还是好好准备高考吧。将来如果真能在学术圈混了，再想着搞个大新闻也不迟。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e刚刚看了一下你的主页，居然已经过千粉了，果然知乎现在韭菜确实好割。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e加油，争取过个万粉，我看好你呦！\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559449958,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"21d88f5ea6bc660dac45f707638b652b","url_token":"lin-sheng-jie-61","name":"动医金城武","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-7bb742da3bea1eb16d578f18337ada05_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-7bb742da3bea1eb16d578f18337ada05_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/21d88f5ea6bc660dac45f707638b652b","user_type":"people","headline":"有证不会治病的学渣","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559449958","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545727905,"updated_time":1546152620,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":5,"content":"\u003cp\u003e不会的\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e因为在古老的东方，有着一个叫做百度贴吧的地方。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e在百度贴吧食物链的顶端有着一群人，被世人称之为键盘侠。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e他们随随便便拉出来一个都能证明这个猜想。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e而且还能顺手玩lol单杀faker；\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e顺手秒速解决所有bug；\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e顺手帮助钢铁侠，把灭霸的宝石抠出来；\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e顺手攒一台预算400rmb，能流畅跑所有3a大作最高画质的电脑；\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e顺手搞一台1000rmb以内，能高帧率高画质吃鸡，拍照秒杀单反，长续航，2k屏幕的手机；\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e顺手指点江山，预测第三次世界大战；\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e……\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e总而言之，再这群人眼里，拯救中国男足都不是事。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e然而这么牛掰的一群人，人均学历都比不过北大青鸟。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e保送清华北大，纯属做梦。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562520519,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"67f9e14548ae31e04dfc101299f6b283","url_token":"miao-tian-yi-73","name":"如月千早","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-cc010fc9edd8d0775b171a3f00bc25ca_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-cc010fc9edd8d0775b171a3f00bc25ca_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/67f9e14548ae31e04dfc101299f6b283","user_type":"people","headline":"生死已看淡，单纵就是干。宠辱应从容，梯形必须怂。","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562520519","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546096247,"updated_time":1546096263,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":5,"content":"\u003cp\u003e不能。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但是可以保送位于北京市西城区德胜街道德外大街西社区的首都医科大学（CMU）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e附属北京安定医院\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563956362,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"d3604c47855458be43f79261b33d14c0","url_token":"lycheer-26","name":"lycheer","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-d60f33c7396af34bc444ddc094a03d20_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-d60f33c7396af34bc444ddc094a03d20_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/d3604c47855458be43f79261b33d14c0","user_type":"people","headline":"目标是 做一个金刚芭比","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563956362","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546315067,"updated_time":1546315067,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":8,"content":"怎么说，我更确信这是一场营销。这个高中生身上存在太多疑点，甚至我怀疑他根本不是高中生。\u003cbr\u003e①他常用错别字。在发表的文章中，“望见谅”写成“忘见谅”，还有一些别的错别字，但是现在文章被他删了，我无法截图。更让人不可思议的是，在他手写的证明过程中，“哥德巴赫猜想”被写成了“歌德巴赫猜想”。当然，有知友说这只是音译问题，无伤大雅。但是他本人再次发表文章，说他的确写错字。\u003cbr\u003e我真的很想问一句，一个高中生，接受了九年义务教育的学生，真的会出现如此高频率的错别字现象吗？\u003cbr\u003e②他装疯卖傻。信誓旦旦地说自己证明了哥猜，于是到知乎来提问，并且扬言要在知乎公布。又吊足大家胃口说1月1日公布证明过程，期间还发表了“如果我届时无法提供证明过程，会怎么样？”的言论，他彻底地秉持着一种调戏的姿态。证明发布出来后，被迅速打脸，半夜删掉自己的证明过程，宣称自己要销号。白天仍然发动态，并且再次发表文章企图证明“我想销号啊，但是知乎不理我，不是我的错”。他作为一个高中生究竟是不会查百度，还是装疯卖傻，大家可以自行定夺。\u003cbr\u003e③他删我评论。在今天早上他发表的文章当中，他说要把自己的证明过程存档起来，以免知友看不见。我是第二个评论的人，我评论的内容如下：销号就销号，不要搞那么多五五六六七七八八的。吃完中午饭回来，我的评论就不见了。为什么要删除我的评论？这个回答就是从你删评这个举动引发的，如果你真的打算销号，你就该拿出你应有的态度和行为，而不是拿出扭扭捏捏的姿态。你可是还在文章里说自己是“河北男人”的，你可记得吗？\u003cbr\u003e④有一个回答说，他的确不是高中生，他已经是一个将近三十岁的“大孩子”了。我不能确定那个回答的真假，当然，那个答主说自己的回答是真的。其实无论他的身份是高中生还是一个三十岁的男人，他的所作所为都让人很无奈。有这个想法与勇气固然是好，但是你如果把它当作是卖弄自己的资本，其实就是对知识的藐视。\u003cbr\u003e最后，取消关注的操作，是必不可少的。","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559978743,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"a4abcb1eac7658b201be03b91a24ce2a","url_token":"","name":"知乎用户","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":true},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559978743","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545798613,"updated_time":1545798825,"extras":"","is_copyable":false,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e第一个夸女人像朵花的是天才，第二个就是蠢材了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这位恐怕真的不如凡伟，凡伟论营销能力恐怕比知乎大部分人都强，他那个群是我见过最活跃最经久不衰的群。里面很多还真是搞科研的高学历人才，虽然只是在里面娱乐。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563822529,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563822529","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-2fd7081e6b7aafb6d74c1b2c70154755_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546285090,"updated_time":1546285090,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":6,"content":"\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-fee5e2e786483d9281220704c84dd3cf_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-fee5e2e786483d9281220704c84dd3cf_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-fee5e2e786483d9281220704c84dd3cf_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1080'%20height='1920'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-fee5e2e786483d9281220704c84dd3cf_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-fee5e2e786483d9281220704c84dd3cf_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-fee5e2e786483d9281220704c84dd3cf_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e就说一个最简单的点，你说你要发表论文，最后出来的是几句话和算草纸，你当真看过任何一篇论文么？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e别以为在河北十八线小城市拿个期中期末数学第一你就漂了，都不用去华师附中，去衡水看看，倒数都能全方位吊打你。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e本来以为，你要在一月一日发布是要做最后论文的编辑调整这些大面儿的活儿，没想到你连论文是什么都不知道。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e井底之蛙，实锤。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560010725,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"09a65cd4227da2d49d40275dfbb5baf0","url_token":"que-zi-que","name":"报时雀仔","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/54f6ac036c34af022a460563dd43268c_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/54f6ac036c34af022a460563dd43268c_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/09a65cd4227da2d49d40275dfbb5baf0","user_type":"people","headline":"一个自以为是的人","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560010725","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545801470,"updated_time":1545801470,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":0,"content":"\u003cp\u003e确定不想去藤校，或者世界第一印度帝国理工吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cvoteup_count%2Ccontent\u0026limit=20\u0026offset=460\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.